<title>UK: Thomas Potts to buy Coalite, make cash call.</title>
<headline>Thomas Potts to buy Coalite, make cash call.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Britain's Thomas Potts Plc said on Thursday it was buying smokeless fuels manufacturer Coalite Products Ltd from Anglo United Plc for 24.3 million stg.</p>
